**The previous download I had up here by accident was the map before this finished one. I have since updated it to the new map. Sorry about that ladies and gents.**



This is version 2 of my previous map "bastille day." I've added a land bridge from the second floor of each spawn building, as well as roof access to this land bridge, with some cover on and inside the bridge, as well as crates to hide behind inside the buildings. Crates have been added behind the Arc for knife fight insanity.
